David Luiz showed he was back in a familiar place on Tuesday ahead of PSG's clash with Chelsea in the Champions League last-16 second leg on Wednesday night.

Luiz returns to Stamford Bridge having played there between 2011 and 2014, and is looking to spoil his former club's chances of reaching the next round.

The Brazil defender posted a photograph on his Instagram and wrote: 'Right time to be back! #LondonCity #Amazing #BigBen #BeautifulDay'.

